Class PinholeToEquirectangular_F64

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    boofcv.struct.distort.PixelTransform

    public class PinholeToEquirectangular_F64
extends EquirectangularDistortBase_F64
    Renders a pinhole camera view from an equirectangular image. When no additional rotation is applied the camera will lie along the +z axis. Before use you must invoke the following functions:
    • setPinhole(boofcv.struct.calib.CameraPinhole)
    • EquirectangularDistortBase_F64.setEquirectangularShape(int, int)
